01:19:54,029 --> 01:19:56,765
Who came up
with all this sick stuff?

1248
01:19:58,133 --> 01:19:59,668
Is this you, Stella?

1249
01:20:00,802 --> 01:20:03,503
We didn't write the stories.

1250
01:20:03,505 --> 01:20:05,507
- (THUNDER RUMBLES)
- (ELECTRICITY CRACKLES)

1251
01:20:08,543 --> 01:20:09,812
(DOG WHINING)

1252
01:20:20,889 --> 01:20:22,424
(DOG GROWLING)

1253
01:20:23,625 --> 01:20:25,161
(THUNDER RUMBLES)

1254
01:20:28,264 --> 01:20:29,766
(LOW GROWLING)

1255
01:20:35,805 --> 01:20:38,208
(LOW GROWLING CONTINUES)

1256
01:20:40,177 --> 01:20:41,611
- Trigger?
- (TRIGGER GROWLS)

1257
01:20:44,615 --> 01:20:45,883
Wait, is there another story?

1258
01:20:46,984 --> 01:20:48,183
Please, you have to
let us out!

1259
01:20:48,185 --> 01:20:49,251
Okay, if there's
another story,

1260
01:20:49,253 --> 01:20:51,055
we are all
gonna be in danger.

1261
01:20:51,822 --> 01:20:54,057
(GROWLING)

1262
01:20:54,059 --> 01:20:55,824
RAMON: Tell us
what's happening!

1263
01:20:55,826 --> 01:20:57,293
STELLA: What's the story?

1264
01:20:57,295 --> 01:20:59,463
(GROWLING IN CADENCE)

1265
01:21:02,167 --> 01:21:03,700
STELLA: Please just listen
to me, okay?

1266
01:21:03,702 --> 01:21:05,802
We're all going to die.

1267
01:21:05,804 --> 01:21:07,905
(TRIGGER GROWLING IN CADENCE)

1268
01:21:16,815 --> 01:21:18,783
(FAINT RUSTLING)

1269
01:21:20,719 --> 01:21:22,318
It's my turn.

1270
01:21:22,320 --> 01:21:25,154
STELLA: Okay,
what happens in the story?

1271
01:21:25,156 --> 01:21:27,058
Just tell me
which name is in the book.

1272
01:21:28,727 --> 01:21:29,894
Ramon.

1273
01:21:30,329 --> 01:21:31,931
(THUNDER CRASHES)

1274
01:21:33,631 --> 01:21:35,034
(BREATHES HEAVILY)

1275
01:21:35,801 --> 01:21:37,570
(TRIGGER GROWLING)

1276
01:21:40,673 --> 01:21:42,773
It's a campfire story.

1277
01:21:42,775 --> 01:21:43,943
It used to scare me
to death.

1278
01:21:45,945 --> 01:21:47,180
(THUNDER CRASHES)

1279
01:21:48,115 --> 01:21:49,580
(WHIMPERS)

1280
01:21:49,582 --> 01:21:50,949
The Jangly Man is coming.

1281
01:21:50,951 --> 01:21:52,017
He's going to take me...

1282
01:21:52,019 --> 01:21:53,351
What's going on?

1283
01:21:53,353 --> 01:21:55,087
RAMON: He's going to say it.
Listen.

1284
01:22:02,695 --> 01:22:06,765
Me tie dough-ty walker!

1285
01:22:06,767 --> 01:22:08,201
Are you shitting me?

1286
01:22:09,903 --> 01:22:11,004
(GASPING)

1287
01:22:14,808 --> 01:22:15,874
(GUN CLICKS)

1288
01:22:15,876 --> 01:22:17,744
(GROWLS)

1289
01:22:18,812 --> 01:22:20,580
(RATTLING)

1290
01:22:29,323 --> 01:22:31,824
Please, just let us out,
please!

1291
01:22:31,826 --> 01:22:32,860
(BONES CRACKING)

1292
01:22:42,938 --> 01:22:45,640
(SNARLING)

1293
01:23:00,289 --> 01:23:01,655
(SNARLS)

1294
01:23:01,657 --> 01:23:02,958
(WHIMPERS)

1295
01:23:04,693 --> 01:23:07,963
JANGLY MAN:
Me tie dough-ty walker!

1296
01:23:08,664 --> 01:23:10,366
(BREATHES SHAKILY)

1297
01:23:11,267 --> 01:23:13,837
(RUSTLING, SCRAPING)

1298
01:23:19,142 --> 01:23:21,211
(BOTH GASPING)

1299
01:23:22,779 --> 01:23:24,147
(GROANING)

1300
01:23:25,449 --> 01:23:27,118
Ramon!

1301
01:23:29,920 --> 01:23:32,019
Ramon.

1302
01:23:32,021 --> 01:23:33,754
STELLA: Oh, my God, Ramon.

1303
01:23:33,756 --> 01:23:34,891
- Oh, my God, what is that?
- (GROWLING)

1304
01:23:38,228 --> 01:23:41,265
Help. Help, please.
Can someone hear me?

1305
01:23:47,304 --> 01:23:48,804
Keys.

1306
01:23:48,806 --> 01:23:49,807
RAMON: Hurry!

1307
01:23:50,708 --> 01:23:51,876
(GROWLING)

1308
01:23:52,409 --> 01:23:53,677
(GRUNTS)

1309
01:23:58,283 --> 01:24:00,918
(GRUNTING)

1310
01:24:06,424 --> 01:24:07,726
Coward!

1311
01:24:10,829 --> 01:24:12,197
STELLA: I got the keys.

1312
01:24:13,899 --> 01:24:15,734
Come on, come on,
come on, come on.

1313
01:24:19,137 --> 01:24:20,172
Coward!

1314
01:24:22,440 --> 01:24:24,209
RAMON: Run! Go, go, go!

1315
01:24:32,951 --> 01:24:34,120
(CHEERING ON TV)

1316
01:24:39,225 --> 01:24:40,960
What are you waiting for?

1317
01:24:41,794 --> 01:24:43,294
Go to the house.

1318
01:24:43,296 --> 01:24:44,529
Tell her the truth.

1319
