Stop her
and you'll stop this.

1323
01:25:00,280 --> 01:25:01,281
(GRUNTS)

1324
01:25:04,419 --> 01:25:05,986
(SNARLS)

1325
01:25:07,354 --> 01:25:08,888
(ENGINE REVVING)

1326
01:25:15,229 --> 01:25:16,230
(GASPS)

1327
01:25:17,231 --> 01:25:19,132
(TIRES SCREECHING)

1328
01:25:21,101 --> 01:25:22,102
(BREATHES HEAVILY)

1329
01:25:29,177 --> 01:25:30,478
(CAR ROOF THUDDING)

1330
01:25:31,980 --> 01:25:33,481
(JANGLY MAN GROWLING)

1331
01:25:40,289 --> 01:25:42,291
- (ENGINE REVVING)
- (TIRES SCREECHING)

1332
01:25:56,538 --> 01:25:57,939
(GROWLS IN PAIN)

1333
01:25:58,973 --> 01:26:00,808
(JANGLY MAN GROANING)

1334
01:26:03,579 --> 01:26:05,314
(CAR DOOR RATTLING)

1335
01:26:11,954 --> 01:26:13,989
(GRUNTING AND GROWLING)

1336
01:26:18,428 --> 01:26:20,297
- (BONES CRACKING)
- (GROANS)

1337
01:26:22,232 --> 01:26:23,400
(BODY THUDS)

1338
01:26:29,205 --> 01:26:30,574
(SCREECHING)

1339
01:26:36,614 --> 01:26:38,247
STELLA: Sarah!

1340
01:26:38,249 --> 01:26:40,349
Can you hear me?

1341
01:26:40,351 --> 01:26:43,485
God damn you!
You have to stop telling these stories!

1342
01:26:43,487 --> 01:26:45,587
We didn't do anything to you!

1343
01:26:45,589 --> 01:26:48,357
We just want to help you!
We know you're innocent!

1344
01:26:48,359 --> 01:26:50,359
We know
you didn't poison the kids!

1345
01:26:50,361 --> 01:26:53,497
(TEARFULLY) But, please,
you just have to stop telling the stories!

1346
01:26:57,335 --> 01:26:59,136
(CLOCK TICKING)

1347
01:27:06,077 --> 01:27:08,946
<i>(YOU MAY BE NEXT</i> PLAYS SOFTLY)

1348
01:27:36,709 --> 01:27:38,344
(FIRE CRACKLING)

1349
01:27:48,454 --> 01:27:50,087
Stella!

1350
01:27:50,089 --> 01:27:51,492
Where are you?

1351
01:27:57,731 --> 01:27:58,998
No, no, no, no.

1352
01:28:00,067 --> 01:28:01,133
Stella.

1353
01:28:01,135 --> 01:28:02,636
(GROWLING IN DISTANCE)

1354
01:28:05,406 --> 01:28:07,040
(GROWLING)

1355
01:28:08,543 --> 01:28:10,543
Stella!

1356
01:28:10,545 --> 01:28:12,612
- (FOOTSTEPS RUNNING)
- (GASPS)

1357
01:28:12,614 --> 01:28:13,648
(FOOTSTEPS FADE)

1358
01:28:20,421 --> 01:28:21,987
(THUNDER RUMBLING)

1359
01:28:21,989 --> 01:28:23,390
- Hey, Stella!
- (JANGLY MAN GROWLS)

1360
01:28:28,128 --> 01:28:29,495
DELANIE: She's out
of her room again.

1361
01:28:29,497 --> 01:28:31,566
DEODAT: Boys? Sarah's out!

1362
01:28:32,434 --> 01:28:34,035
Find her now!

1363
01:28:35,036 --> 01:28:36,037
HAROLD: Sarah!

1364
01:28:37,138 --> 01:28:38,973
- (CHANDELIER CLINKING)
- (GROWLING)

1365
01:28:40,408 --> 01:28:41,677
(PANTING)

1366
01:28:44,413 --> 01:28:45,614
HAROLD: Sarah!

1367
01:28:48,384 --> 01:28:50,586
You leave that to me, Harold.

1368
01:28:54,190 --> 01:28:55,591
HAROLD: Sarah!

1369
01:28:57,426 --> 01:28:59,028
DEODAT: Sarah, where are you?

1370
01:29:02,432 --> 01:29:03,500
(DOOR CLOSES)

1371
01:29:06,570 --> 01:29:08,170
HAROLD: Sarah!

1372
01:29:09,371 --> 01:29:10,739
(BREATH TREMBLING)

1373
01:29:14,611 --> 01:29:16,212
(BREATHING SHAKILY)

1374
01:29:21,351 --> 01:29:23,151
GERTRUDE: I hear her.

1375
01:29:23,153 --> 01:29:25,188
(OPERATIC MUSIC PLAYING)

1376
01:29:29,292 --> 01:29:30,761
(BREATH TREMBLING)

1377
01:29:31,528 --> 01:29:33,129
She's here!

1378
01:29:34,699 --> 01:29:36,501
She's in here!

1379
01:29:40,271 --> 01:29:41,405
(WHIMPERS)

1380
01:29:45,811 --> 01:29:47,409
(SNARLS)

1381
01:29:47,411 --> 01:29:49,345
(BANGING ON DOOR)

1382
01:29:49,347 --> 01:29:50,682
(GASPING)

1383
01:29:55,520 --> 01:29:56,521
EPHRAIM: Sarah!

1384
01:29:59,156 --> 01:30:00,191
Where are you?

1385
01:30:06,732 --> 01:30:07,733
STELLA: Lou Lou.

1386
01:30:11,803 --> 01:30:12,804
(DOOR RATTLES)

1387
01:30:21,446 --> 01:30:23,081
(GROANS, PANTS)

1388
01:30:25,250 --> 01:30:26,316
DELANIE: Did you see Sarah?

1389
01:30:26,318 --> 01:30:27,451
YOUNG LOU LOU: (PANTS)
No, ma'am.

1390
01:30:27,453 --> 01:30:28,519
HAROLD: She's lying.

1391
01:30:28,521 --> 01:30:32,189
DELANIE: You wouldn't lie,
Lou Lou?

1392
01:30:32,191 --> 01:30:33,257
YOUNG LOU LOU: No, ma'am.

1393
01:30:33,259 --> 01:30:34,525
No, I didn't see Sarah.

1394
01:30:34,527 --> 01:30:36,594
No, Mr. Bellows, please, no!

1395
01:30:36,596 --> 01:30:38,262
Please, no!

1396
01:30:38,264 --> 01:30:39,633
(THUNDER RUMBLING)

1397
01:31:08,729 --> 01:31:09,763
You can't hide from us.

1398
01:31:10,564 --> 01:31:11,630
HAROLD: Got you!

1399
01:31:11,632 --> 01:31:13,933
No! No!

1400
01:31:13,935 --> 01:31:16,301
Help me! Help me!

1401
01:31:16,303 --> 01:31:18,338
- STELLA: Help me!
- Stella!

1402
01:31:18,340 --> 01:31:21,341
STELLA: Please! Help me!

1403
01:31:21,343 --> 01:31:23,343
- Please, help me!
- EPHRAIM: She's been telling everyone about the water.

1404
01:31:23,345 --> 01:31:24,410
DELANIE: What should
we do with her?

1405
01:31:24,412 --> 01:31:25,812
Somebody, help me, please.

1406
01:31:25,814 --> 01:31:26,947
You're going to shut your ugly mouth
or we're going to shut it for you.

1407
01:31:26,949 --> 01:31:29,282
Please, help me!

1408
01:31:29,284 --> 01:31:32,119
- (JANGLY MAN GROWLING)
- STELLA: Help me, please!

1409
01:31:36,658 --> 01:31:38,324
DEODAT: Going back
where you belong.

1410
01:31:38,326 --> 01:31:39,959
STELLA: (SOBBING)
Help me, please.

1411
01:31:39,961 --> 01:31:42,197
DELANIE: Be quiet
or you know what you'll get.

1412
01:31:43,698 --> 01:31:46,599
Please. I'm not Sarah. Please!

1413
01:31:46,601 --> 01:31:48,738
Please let me go. Please...

1414
01:31:49,472 --> 01:31:50,840
Let me go.

1415
01:31:52,274 --> 01:31:53,507
Please, don't put me in here.

1416
01:31:53,509 --> 01:31:55,676
HAROLD: Try this again and
we'll send you to the asylum.

1417
01:31:55,678 --> 01:31:58,612
STELLA: Please. Wait! Please?

1418
01:31:58,614 --> 01:32:00,547
DELANIE: You should have
stayed in your room.

1419
01:32:00,549 --> 01:32:02,917
(SOBBING)
Please. Please. Please.

1420
01:32:02,919 --> 01:32:04,019
I didn't do it.

1421
01:32:04,021 --> 01:32:05,954
- DELANIE: You don't deserve the light.
- (SWITCH CLICKS)

1422
01:32:05,956 --> 01:32:07,289
No!

1423
01:32:08,792 --> 01:32:11,559
I'm telling you,
I'm telling you,

1424
01:32:11,561 --> 01:32:13,363
I'm not Sarah.

1425
01:32:14,598 --> 01:32:15,697
Please.

1426
01:32:15,699 --> 01:32:16,868
(MUFFLED THUD)

1427
01:32:19,736 --> 01:32:21,437
(CONTINUES SOBBING)

1428
01:32:29,846 --> 01:32:31,715
- (SOFT TAPPING)
- (SOBBING STOPS)

1429
01:33:00,446 --> 01:33:02,414
- (SARAH BREATHING SHAKILY)
- (CHAIR CREAKS)

1430
01:33:03,348 --> 01:33:05,384
(WHIMPERING SOFTLY)

1431
01:33:07,552 --> 01:33:09,220
(BOOK THUDS)

1432
01:33:18,464 --> 01:33:20,599
<i>(YOU MAY BE NEXT</i> PLAYS SOFTLY)

1433
01:33:24,670 --> 01:33:26,271
SARAH: (WHISPERS) Stella...

1434
01:33:30,910 --> 01:33:31,945
(GASPS)

1435
01:33:41,488 --> 01:33:43,922
I have another story

1436
01:33:43,924 --> 01:33:45,525
just for you.

1437
01:33:47,360 --> 01:33:48,763
(SNARLING)

1438
01:33:51,999 --> 01:33:53,267
Stella,

1439
01:33:55,335 --> 01:33:58,338
if you can hear me,
wherever you are,

1440
01:33:59,372 --> 01:34:01,341
tell her the truth.

1441
01:34:07,414 --> 01:34:08,249
No.

1442
01:34:10,851 --> 01:34:13,521
It's time that
you hear a story, Sarah.

1443
01:34:17,726 --> 01:34:19,326
You were a victim.

1444
01:34:20,729 --> 01:34:23,330
Now you've turned
into a monster.

1445
01:34:24,699 --> 01:34:26,902
The one that
they said you were.

1446
01:34:35,978 --> 01:34:36,979
Stella.

1447
01:34:38,681 --> 01:34:40,449
You took my friends.

1448
01:34:42,018 --> 01:34:44,452
Two of the people
that I love most.

1449
01:34:46,055 --> 01:34:47,422
(PANTING)

1450
01:34:53,029 --> 01:34:54,597
Ramon!

1451
01:34:54,997 --> 01:34:56,463
(GROWLS)

1452
01:34:56,465 --> 01:34:57,631
RAMON: (MUFFLED) Stella!

1453
01:34:57,633 --> 01:34:59,033
(BREATH TREMBLING)

1454
01:34:59,035 --> 01:35:00,770
Are you going
to take him, too?

1455
01:35:01,871 --> 01:35:03,873
What your family
did to you,

1456
01:35:04,975 --> 01:35:06,576
what they said,
that's on them.

1457
01:35:08,644 --> 01:35:09,980
But what you do,

1458
01:35:12,616 --> 01:35:14,350
this is on you, Sarah.

1459
01:35:17,888 --> 01:35:18,956
It's all on you.

1460
01:35:22,927 --> 01:35:24,762
(WHIMPERS SOFTLY)

1461
01:35:27,497 --> 01:35:29,000
I'll tell your story.

1462
01:35:31,735 --> 01:35:33,937
The real story,
I'll tell the truth.

1463
01:35:37,741 --> 01:35:38,775
But the rage,

1464
01:35:39,843 --> 01:35:42,412
the rage has to stop, Sarah.

1465
01:35:59,664 --> 01:36:00,666
(GASPS)

1466
01:36:03,569 --> 01:36:04,970
Use your blood.

1467
01:36:17,050 --> 01:36:18,449
(STELLA GRUNTS)

1468
01:36:27,927 --> 01:36:31,062
Sarah Bellows was innocent.

1469
01:36:31,064 --> 01:36:33,432
She knew the truth,

1470
01:36:34,533 --> 01:36:36,267
and tried to stop them.

1471
01:36:36,269 --> 01:36:37,469
She was brave.

1472
01:36:38,138 --> 01:36:41,005
She was harmed and destroyed

1473
01:36:41,007 --> 01:36:43,608
by her own family.

1474
01:36:43,610 --> 01:36:45,478
By their greed,

1475
01:36:46,080 --> 01:36:48,513
and their lies

1476
01:36:48,515 --> 01:36:49,850
and their sins.

1477
01:36:52,253 --> 01:36:53,788
I'll tell your story.

1478
01:36:56,958 --> 01:36:58,559
(BREATHING SHAKILY)

1479
01:36:59,060 --> 01:37:00,628
You can let it go.

1480
01:37:02,897 --> 01:37:04,232
You can let it go, Sarah.

1481
01:37:13,941 --> 01:37:16,043
(SHRIEKING LOUDLY)

1482
01:37:19,081 --> 01:37:20,115
(GROWLS)

1483
01:37:21,615 --> 01:37:22,849
(GASPING)

1484
01:37:22,851 --> 01:37:24,985
(RUMBLING)

1485
01:37:24,987 --> 01:37:26,219
(RUMBLING STOPS)

1486
01:37:26,221 --> 01:37:27,923
(WHIMPERING)

1487
01:37:41,104 --> 01:37:42,737
(BREATHES HEAVILY)

1488
01:37:42,739 --> 01:37:44,107
(THUNDER RUMBLING)

1489
01:37:46,275 --> 01:37:47,577
(EXHALES SHARPLY)

1490
01:37:49,779 --> 01:37:51,181
STELLA: <i>Stories hurt.</i>

1491
01:37:51,914 --> 01:37:53,516
<i>Stories heal.</i>

1492
01:37:57,153 --> 01:37:59,720
<i>If we repeat them
often enough,</i>

1493
01:37:59,722 --> 01:38:00,723
<i>they become real.</i>

1494
01:38:01,591 --> 01:38:03,026
<i>They have that power.</i>

1495
01:38:06,929 --> 01:38:08,363
<i>They make us who we are.</i>

1496
01:38:08,365 --> 01:38:09,630
RAMON: Stella.

1497
01:38:09,632 --> 01:38:11,301
STELLA: I'm just so happy
you're okay.

1498
01:38:24,081 --> 01:38:27,118
STELLA: <i>And if there's
anything I learned from Sarah,</i>

